---
title: Savoury Mushroom Risotto with Roasted Broccoli
description: Let us introduce you to: risotto made easy! Miso broth concentrate packs a flavour punch in this umami-rich risotto full of earthy mushrooms and Parmesan cheese. The meal is made complete with a hearty side of roasted broccoli.
